Type: Package
Package: wdi2
Title: Download World Development Indicators from the World Bank
        Indicators API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c( person("Christoph", "Scheuch", ,
        "christoph.scheuch@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment
        = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0423-6819")) )
Description: A modern, flexible interface for accessing the World
        Bank’s World Development Indicators (WDI) API
        <https://datahelpdesk.worldbank.org/knowledgebase/articles/889392-about-the-indicators-api-documentation>.
        Similar to the existing 'WDI' package, 'wdi2' allows users to
        download, process, and analyze indicator data for multiple
        countries and years. However, 'wdi2' differs by relying on
        'httr2' for multi-page request and error handling, providing
        support for downloading multiple indicators with a single
        function call, using progress bars to keep users informed about
        the data processing, and returning the processed data in a tidy
        data format in line with Wickham (2014)
        <doi:10.18637/jss.v059.i10>.
